title: THE BOB HOPE SPECIAL -- NBC comedians on strike
description:
An all-star spoof of censorship for the entire hour includes only famous male comedians including George Gobel, Flip Wilson, Marty Allen, Steve Allen, 
Shelley Berman, Red Buttons, Sid Caesar, Johnny Carson, Jerry Colonna, Wally Cox, Bill Dana, Richard Deacon, Shecky Greene, Buddy Hackett, Jack E. Leonard, Pat Paulsen, Nipsey Russell, Soupy Sales, Phil Silvers, Danny Thomas, 
Chet Huntley and David Brinkley ( they're not comedians but NBC news anchors ), 
The Smothers Brothers, Jack Carter, Rowan & Martin, and Jimmy Durante.
